\chapter{LaTeX Integration}

The PythonTeX integration is where the design becomes visible to end users.
The helper functions must do both the side-effect work of registration and QR
generation, and the presentational work of emitting LaTeX that fits naturally
either into a Beamer slide or into the book-style manual.

